---
// /for-medspa/ — vertical lander for med-spa / aesthetic clinics (Phase 5, 2026-05-04)
// Dollar impact: high LTV per client ($2K-$10K), severe voicemail leak, brutal review competition
// Vocabulary: membership, package, consultation, before/after, treatment series, retention
// Stack: Boulevard, Aesthetics Pro, Vagaro, Mindbody, Mangomint
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="For med-spa &amp; aesthetic clinics &mdash; Memberships, missed consultations, missed reviews"
  description="AI customer lifecycle for med-spa and aesthetic clinics across Canada and the United States. Membership reactivation, missed-consultation rescue, package upsell automation, before/after review velocity. Wraps around Boulevard, Aesthetics Pro, Vagaro, Mindbody. HIPAA BAA on request. A service of Agni Consulting."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="ai-hero">
    <p class="ai-eyebrow">FOR MED-SPA &amp; AESTHETIC CLINICS</p>
    <h1>Your average client is worth <br>$3,000+. <br>Your phone is at voicemail.</h1>
    <p class="ai-lead">
      Med-spa and aesthetic clients have lifetime values from $2,000 (one-and-done injectable) to $10,000+ (membership over multiple years). Every missed call is a multi-thousand-dollar shrug. Industry voicemail rates hit 30%+ in season. Your membership program has churn nobody&rsquo;s actively fighting. Your before/after photos sit in Boulevard or Vagaro &mdash; the chain across the river is collecting Google reviews on autopilot, you aren&rsquo;t.
    </p>
    <p class="ai-lead" style="font-weight:600;color:var(--tx);">
      We run membership reactivation, missed-consultation rescue, package upsell sequences, and before/after review automation. Wraps around your booking software. HIPAA BAA on request. Done-for-you, by operators.
    </p>
    <div class="ai-cta-row">
      <a class="ai-btn" href="https://calendly.com/aman-shopagni" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book a free Growth Audit &rarr;</a>
      <a class="ai-btn-ghost" href="/engagements/">Engagement shapes</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain bullets -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap ai-narrow">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow">Sound like your spa?</p>
      <h2>The high-LTV leak.</h2>
      <ul class="ai-painlist" style="font-size:17px;margin-top:24px;">
        <li>"Our consultation no-show rate is 25%+. Each one is a $3,000 conversation we&rsquo;ll never have again."</li>
        <li>"Our membership churn is double-digits. We don&rsquo;t have a save sequence."</li>
        <li>"We have 600 clients who haven&rsquo;t booked in nine months. We send a generic email blast once a quarter and call it a day."</li>
        <li>"Treatment series like CoolSculpting, Sculptra, microneedling &mdash; clients drop off after session 2 of 4. Nobody follows up."</li>
        <li>"Our Google review count is 80. The med-spa eight blocks away has 1,400. It&rsquo;s a nightmare for ad performance."</li>
        <li>"Our front desk is one person. She handles consults, intake, calls, and rebooking. Things slip."</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top:32px;color:var(--tx-soft);font-size:16px;">
        At your ticket sizes, even a 10% lift on any of these is six figures a year. The dollar math here is the most aggressive in the service-business universe.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What we run -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">What we run for you</p>
      <h2 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">Five systems. Wraps around your booking software. Respects medical-aesthetic advertising rules.</h2>
      <div class="ai-grid-2">

        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>1. Membership reactivation + churn save</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--tx-soft);">Tracks membership cancellations and proactively reaches out to lapsed members 30 / 60 / 90 days post-cancel. Win-back sequence with personalized offer based on treatment history. Member benefits: 256% more revenue per active member than non-member &mdash; protecting the membership base is the single highest-leverage move.</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Pre-cancel save sequence triggered on cancel-attempt</li>
            <li>Post-cancel win-back at 30/60/90 days</li>
            <li>Membership renewal reminders</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>2. Missed-consultation rescue</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--tx-soft);">No-show on a consultation = $3K-$10K of treatment-plan revenue gone. We send SMS within 5 minutes of no-show, offer same-week reschedule, and follow up at 48 hrs and 7 days. Plus reminder sequences before consultations to suppress no-shows in the first place.</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Pre-consultation reminder cadence (7d / 24h / 2h)</li>
            <li>Same-day no-show rescue SMS</li>
            <li>48-hour and 7-day follow-up</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>3. Package + treatment-series completion</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--tx-soft);">Tracks every package and multi-session treatment series. Reminds the client at the right interval to book the next session. Sends education and pre-care content between sessions to keep momentum. Series completion rate typically lifts from ~50% to 70%+.</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Per-treatment series tracking</li>
            <li>Timed re-booking reminders</li>
            <li>Pre-care + post-care educational SMS</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>4. Before/after review velocity</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--tx-soft);">Post-treatment SMS review request, timed for visible-result window (immediate for facials, 1-2 weeks for injectables, 6-8 weeks for energy-based treatments). Negative feedback intercepted privately. Spas typically add 50-150 Google reviews in 90 days &mdash; the gap with chain spas closes meaningfully.</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Treatment-aware review request timing</li>
            <li>Provincial / state aesthetic-medicine advertising rules respected</li>
            <li>Photo/testimonial consent capture in-flow</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>5. Owner dashboard</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--tx-soft);">One screen: membership net retention, consultation no-show rate, treatment series completion, review velocity, recovered revenue. Per-provider revenue split. Monthly PDF for the practice meeting.</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Membership net-retention dashboard</li>
            <li>Per-provider revenue splits</li>
            <li>Recovered-revenue calculation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-card" style="border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-soft);">
          <h3 style="color:var(--accent);">Built around your software.</h3>
          <p>Boulevard, Aesthetics Pro, Vagaro, Mindbody, Mangomint &mdash; we wrap around all of them. Your front desk keeps using what they know. We fill the lifecycle gaps your booking software was never designed to fill.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Engagement shapes -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">Engagement shapes</p>
      <h2 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:8px;">Three shapes. Audit first. Most med-spas start with a Pilot focused on memberships.</h2>
      <p style="text-align:center;color:var(--tx-soft);margin-bottom:32px;max-width:640px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
        Engagements typically range from low-four-figures to mid-four-figures monthly (USD). With $2K-$10K ticket sizes, the math is the most aggressive in our portfolio.
      </p>
      <div class="ai-tiers">

        <article class="ai-tier">
          <h3>1. Free Growth Audit</h3>
          <p class="ai-tier-tagline">Diagnose, free</p>
          <p class="ai-tier-price" style="font-size:24px;">Free</p>
          <p class="ai-tier-price-sub">30 min &middot; one-page leak report in 24 hrs</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Live walk-through of your booking software</li>
            <li>Membership churn + dormant-client analysis</li>
            <li>Consultation no-show rate review</li>
            <li>One-page leak report ranked by recoverable revenue</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="ai-btn-ghost" href="https://calendly.com/aman-shopagni" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">Book audit &rarr;</a>
        </article>

        <article class="ai-tier ai-tier-featured">
          <h3>2. Pilot</h3>
          <p class="ai-tier-tagline">Most med-spas start here</p>
          <p class="ai-tier-price" style="font-size:24px;">60 days, fixed scope</p>
          <p class="ai-tier-price-sub">See dollar impact before any monthly commitment</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Membership save + win-back sequences live</li>
            <li>Missed-consultation rescue automation</li>
            <li>Treatment-series completion tracking</li>
            <li>Weekly check-in for 60 days</li>
            <li>End-of-pilot dollar-impact report</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="ai-btn" href="https://calendly.com/aman-shopagni" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">Book audit &rarr;</a>
        </article>

        <article class="ai-tier">
          <h3>3. Run-It</h3>
          <p class="ai-tier-tagline">Done-for-you, end-to-end</p>
          <p class="ai-tier-price" style="font-size:24px;">Monthly retainer</p>
          <p class="ai-tier-price-sub">Cancel any time after first 90 days</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Full lifecycle: memberships, consultations, packages, reviews, after-hours</li>
            <li>AI voice receptionist 24/7</li>
            <li>Custom integrations with your booking software</li>
            <li>Dedicated ops contact, weekly check-in</li>
            <li>Quarterly strategy session with senior operator</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="ai-btn-ghost" href="https://calendly.com/aman-shopagni" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">Book audit &rarr;</a>
        </article>

      </div>
      <p style="text-align:center;color:var(--tx-soft);margin-top:24px;font-size:14px;">AmSpa &middot; ASAPS &middot; provincial / state aesthetic-medicine advertising rules respected. HIPAA BAA on request. Full pricing on the audit call.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="ai-section-tight">
    <div class="ai-wrap ai-narrow" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2>30-min audit. We pull your membership churn, your consultation no-shows, your dormant list.</h2>
      <p class="ai-lead">No deck, no pitch. The leak report is yours to keep even if you never hire us.</p>
      <div class="ai-cta-row">
        <a class="ai-btn" href="https://calendly.com/aman-shopagni" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book the audit &rarr;</a>
        <a class="ai-btn-ghost" href="/about/">About the team</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
